spells.description: Use: Fashion nearby garbage into a sphere and launch it into the sky. After 3 sec of gathering momentum the sphere crashes into the targeted location dealing 2 million Physical damage split between all enemies in the area. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Falling below 60% health surrounds you with a protective vortex of junk, reducing damage taken by 50% for 15 sec or until 1.2 million damage is prevented. This effect may only occur every 30 sec.

After 20 sec without activating while in combat, the Scrapfield overloads to energize you with 2,987 Haste for 12 sec.
Valid only for tank specializations.
Equip: Your attacks have a very high chance to contaminate your target with industrial runoff up to 25 times, dealing 1,793 Shadow damage per stack every 3 sec until their demise.
